Declaration

We are pleased to report that there is a 0% gender pay gap within our flexible workforce, who we employ 
to provide excellent service to our valued clients. I confirm that our data has been calculated according to 
the requirements of The Equality Act 2010 (Gender Pay Gap Information) Regulations 2017.
